<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<search>
  <entry>
    <title>Mysql常用日期生成</title>
    <url>/2024/01/05/Mysql%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>有时我们在生成一些时间轴类似的数据时，要求数据库不管有没有指定天的数据，都要生成该时间节点，可用mysql.help_topic来解决此类问题，通过序列和日期函数相结合来满足我们的业务需求。 </p>
</blockquote>
<span id="more"></span>

<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-- 今天</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">(NOW()</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d 00:00:00&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;今天开始&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">(NOW()</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d 23:59:59&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;今天结束&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- 昨天</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( DATE_SUB(CURDATE()</span>, INTERVAL <span class="number">1</span> DAY), <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d 00:00:00&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;昨天开始&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( DATE_SUB(CURDATE()</span>, INTERVAL <span class="number">1</span> DAY), <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d 23:59:59&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;昨天结束&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- 上周</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( DATE_SUB( DATE_SUB(CURDATE()</span>, INTERVAL <span class="title function_">WEEKDAY</span><span class="params">(CURDATE()</span>) DAY), INTERVAL <span class="number">1</span> WEEK), <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d 00:00:00&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;上周一&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( SUBDATE(CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY(CURDATE()) + <span class="number">1</span>), <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d 23:59:59&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;上周末&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- 本周</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( SUBDATE(CURDATE()</span>,DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE(),<span class="string">&#x27;%w&#x27;</span>)-<span class="number">1</span>), <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d 00:00:00&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;本周一&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( SUBDATE(CURDATE()</span>,DATE_FORMAT(CURDATE(),<span class="string">&#x27;%w&#x27;</span>)-<span class="number">7</span>), <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d 23:59:59&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;本周末&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">-- 上面的本周算法会有问题,因为mysql是按照周日为一周第一天,如果当前是周日的话,会把时间定为到下一周.</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( DATE_SUB(CURDATE()</span>, INTERVAL <span class="title function_">WEEKDAY</span><span class="params">(CURDATE()</span>) DAY), <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d 00:00:00&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;本周一&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( DATE_ADD(SUBDATE(CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY(CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">6</span> DAY), <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d 23:59:59&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;本周末&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- 上月</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( DATE_SUB(CURDATE()</span>, INTERVAL <span class="number">1</span> MONTH), <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-01 00:00:00&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;上月初&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( LAST_DAY(DATE_SUB(CURDATE()</span>, INTERVAL <span class="number">1</span> MONTH)), <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d 23:59:59&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;上月末&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-- 本月</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( CURDATE()</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-01 00:00:00&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;本月初&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( LAST_DAY(CURDATE()</span>), <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d 23:59:59&#x27;</span>) AS <span class="string">&#x27;本月末&#x27;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="1、计算当日净收入"><a href="#1、计算当日净收入" class="headerlink" title="1、计算当日净收入"></a>1、计算当日净收入</h1><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">sum</span>(IF( order_status <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">1</span>, amount, <span class="number">0</span> ))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">-</span> <span class="built_in">sum</span>(IF( order_status <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">8</span>, amount, <span class="number">0</span> )) current_day_m</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span></span><br><span class="line">	`t_pay_details` </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">WHERE</span></span><br><span class="line">	DATE_FORMAT( status_time, <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span> ) <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;2022-07-26&#x27;</span> </span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">AND</span> order_status <span class="operator">&lt;&gt;</span> <span class="number">3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h1 id="2、计算本周的净收入"><a href="#2、计算本周的净收入" class="headerlink" title="2、计算本周的净收入"></a>2、计算本周的净收入</h1><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">SELECT</span><br><span class="line">	a.curdate,</span><br><span class="line">	IFNULL( b.current_day_m, <span class="number">0</span> )/ <span class="number">100</span> current_day_m </span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">FROM</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="params">(</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">	SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">		DATE_SUB( CURDATE()</span>, INTERVAL <span class="title function_">WEEKDAY</span><span class="params">( CURDATE()</span>) DAY ) AS curdate UNION</span><br><span class="line">	SELECT</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">( SUBDATE( CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">1</span> DAY ) AS curdate UNION</span><br><span class="line">	SELECT</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">( SUBDATE( CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">2</span> DAY ) AS curdate UNION</span><br><span class="line">	SELECT</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">( SUBDATE( CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">3</span> DAY ) AS curdate UNION</span><br><span class="line">	SELECT</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">( SUBDATE( CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">4</span> DAY ) AS curdate UNION</span><br><span class="line">	SELECT</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">( SUBDATE( CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">5</span> DAY ) AS curdate UNION</span><br><span class="line">	SELECT</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">( SUBDATE( CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">6</span> DAY ) </span><br><span class="line">	) a</span><br><span class="line">	LEFT <span class="title function_">JOIN</span> <span class="params">(</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">	SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">		DATE_FORMAT( status_time, <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span> )</span> curdate,</span><br><span class="line">		sum(</span><br><span class="line">		IF</span><br><span class="line">			( order_status = <span class="number">1</span>, amount, <span class="number">0</span> )) - sum(</span><br><span class="line">		IF</span><br><span class="line">		( order_status = <span class="number">8</span>, amount, <span class="number">0</span> )) current_day_m </span><br><span class="line">	FROM</span><br><span class="line">		`t_pay_details` </span><br><span class="line">	WHERE</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( status_time, <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span> )</span> BETWEEN ( SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_SUB</span><span class="params">( CURDATE()</span>, INTERVAL <span class="title function_">WEEKDAY</span><span class="params">( CURDATE()</span>) DAY ) AS curdate ) </span><br><span class="line">		AND (</span><br><span class="line">		SELECT</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">( SUBDATE( CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">6</span> DAY )) </span><br><span class="line">		AND order_status &lt;&gt; <span class="number">3</span> </span><br><span class="line">	GROUP BY</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( status_time, <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span> )</span> </span><br><span class="line">	) b ON a.curdate = b.curdate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h1 id="3、获取本周（周一到周日）"><a href="#3、获取本周（周一到周日）" class="headerlink" title="3、获取本周（周一到周日）"></a>3、获取本周（周一到周日）</h1><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_SUB</span><span class="params">(CURDATE()</span>, INTERVAL <span class="title function_">WEEKDAY</span><span class="params">(CURDATE()</span>) DAY) AS <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span> union</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">(SUBDATE(CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY(CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">1</span> DAY) AS <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span> union</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">(SUBDATE(CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY(CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">2</span> DAY) AS <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span> union</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">(SUBDATE(CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY(CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">3</span> DAY) AS <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span> union</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">(SUBDATE(CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY(CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">4</span> DAY) AS <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span> union</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">(SUBDATE(CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY(CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">5</span> DAY) AS <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span> union</span><br><span class="line">SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_ADD</span><span class="params">(SUBDATE(CURDATE()</span>, WEEKDAY(CURDATE())), INTERVAL <span class="number">6</span> DAY)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="4、获取本月的所有天数"><a href="#4、获取本月的所有天数" class="headerlink" title="4、获取本月的所有天数"></a>4、获取本月的所有天数</h1><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">SELECT</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="title function_">date_format</span><span class="params">(</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">		date_add( DATE_ADD( curdate()</span>, INTERVAL - DAY ( curdate())+ <span class="number">1</span> DAY ), INTERVAL ( cast( help_topic_id AS signed INTEGER ) + <span class="number">0</span> ) DAY ),</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span> </span><br><span class="line">	) curdate</span><br><span class="line">FROM</span><br><span class="line">	mysql.help_topic </span><br><span class="line">WHERE</span><br><span class="line">	help_topic_id &lt; DAY (</span><br><span class="line">		last_day(</span><br><span class="line">		DATE_ADD( curdate(), INTERVAL - DAY ( curdate())+ <span class="number">1</span> DAY ))) </span><br><span class="line">ORDER BY</span><br><span class="line">	help_topic_id;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h1 id="5、获取本月的净收入"><a href="#5、获取本月的净收入" class="headerlink" title="5、获取本月的净收入"></a>5、获取本月的净收入</h1><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">explain select SQL_NO_CACHE a.curdate,IFNULL( b.current_day_m, <span class="number">0</span> )/ <span class="number">100</span>  current_day_m <span class="title function_">from</span> <span class="params">(SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">	date_format(</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">		date_add( DATE_ADD( curdate()</span>, INTERVAL - DAY ( curdate())+ <span class="number">1</span> DAY ), INTERVAL ( cast( help_topic_id AS signed INTEGER ) + <span class="number">0</span> ) DAY ),</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span> </span><br><span class="line">	) curdate</span><br><span class="line">FROM</span><br><span class="line">	mysql.help_topic </span><br><span class="line">WHERE</span><br><span class="line">	help_topic_id &lt; DAY (</span><br><span class="line">		last_day(</span><br><span class="line">		DATE_ADD( curdate(), INTERVAL - DAY ( curdate())+ <span class="number">1</span> DAY ))) </span><br><span class="line">ORDER BY</span><br><span class="line">	help_topic_id) a</span><br><span class="line">LEFT <span class="title function_">JOIN</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">(</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">		DATE_FORMAT( status_time, <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span> )</span> curdate,</span><br><span class="line">		sum(</span><br><span class="line">		IF</span><br><span class="line">			( order_status = <span class="number">1</span>, amount, <span class="number">0</span> )) - sum(</span><br><span class="line">		IF</span><br><span class="line">		( order_status = <span class="number">8</span>, amount, <span class="number">0</span> )) current_day_m </span><br><span class="line">	FROM</span><br><span class="line">		`t_pay_details` </span><br><span class="line">	WHERE</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">(status_time, <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span> )</span> BETWEEN ( SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( CURDATE()</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-01&#x27;</span>) ) </span><br><span class="line">		AND (SELECT <span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">(LAST_DAY(CURDATE()</span>), <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span>)) </span><br><span class="line">		AND order_status &lt;&gt; <span class="number">3</span> </span><br><span class="line">	GROUP BY</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="title function_">DATE_FORMAT</span><span class="params">( status_time, <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span> )</span> </span><br><span class="line">) b ON a.curdate = b.curdate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="6、计算上周每一天的净收入"><a href="#6、计算上周每一天的净收入" class="headerlink" title="6、计算上周每一天的净收入"></a>6、计算上周每一天的净收入</h1><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">	a.curdate,</span><br><span class="line">	IFNULL( b.current_day_m, <span class="number">0</span> )<span class="operator">/</span> <span class="number">100</span>  current_day_m</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span></span><br><span class="line">	(</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">		DATE_SUB( SUBDATE( CURDATE(), WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), <span class="type">INTERVAL</span> <span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">DAY</span> ) <span class="keyword">AS</span> curdate <span class="keyword">UNION</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">		DATE_SUB( SUBDATE( CURDATE(), WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), <span class="type">INTERVAL</span> <span class="number">2</span> <span class="keyword">DAY</span> ) <span class="keyword">AS</span> curdate <span class="keyword">UNION</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">		DATE_SUB( SUBDATE( CURDATE(), WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), <span class="type">INTERVAL</span> <span class="number">3</span> <span class="keyword">DAY</span> ) <span class="keyword">AS</span> curdate <span class="keyword">UNION</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">		DATE_SUB( SUBDATE( CURDATE(), WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), <span class="type">INTERVAL</span> <span class="number">4</span> <span class="keyword">DAY</span> ) <span class="keyword">AS</span> curdate <span class="keyword">UNION</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">		DATE_SUB( SUBDATE( CURDATE(), WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), <span class="type">INTERVAL</span> <span class="number">5</span> <span class="keyword">DAY</span> ) <span class="keyword">AS</span> curdate <span class="keyword">UNION</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">		DATE_SUB( SUBDATE( CURDATE(), WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), <span class="type">INTERVAL</span> <span class="number">6</span> <span class="keyword">DAY</span> ) <span class="keyword">AS</span> curdate <span class="keyword">UNION</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">		DATE_SUB( SUBDATE( CURDATE(), WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), <span class="type">INTERVAL</span> <span class="number">7</span> <span class="keyword">DAY</span> )</span><br><span class="line">	) a</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">LEFT</span> <span class="keyword">JOIN</span> (</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">		DATE_FORMAT( status_time, <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span> ) curdate,</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="built_in">sum</span>(</span><br><span class="line">		IF</span><br><span class="line">			( order_status <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">1</span>, amount, <span class="number">0</span> )) <span class="operator">-</span> <span class="built_in">sum</span>(</span><br><span class="line">		IF</span><br><span class="line">		( order_status <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">8</span>, amount, <span class="number">0</span> )) current_day_m </span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">FROM</span></span><br><span class="line">		`t_pay_details` </span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">WHERE</span></span><br><span class="line">		DATE_FORMAT( status_time, <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span> ) <span class="keyword">BETWEEN</span> 		( <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> DATE_SUB( SUBDATE( CURDATE(), WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), <span class="type">INTERVAL</span> <span class="number">7</span> <span class="keyword">DAY</span> ) <span class="keyword">AS</span> curdate )</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">AND</span> </span><br><span class="line">		( <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> DATE_SUB( SUBDATE( CURDATE(), WEEKDAY( CURDATE())), <span class="type">INTERVAL</span> <span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">DAY</span> ) <span class="keyword">AS</span> curdate ) </span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">AND</span> order_status <span class="operator">&lt;&gt;</span> <span class="number">3</span> </span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">GROUP</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span></span><br><span class="line">	DATE_FORMAT( status_time, <span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span> ) </span><br><span class="line">	) b <span class="keyword">ON</span> a.curdate <span class="operator">=</span> b.curdate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="7、先按a字段排序，a字段相同按b字段，最后计算排名"><a href="#7、先按a字段排序，a字段相同按b字段，最后计算排名" class="headerlink" title="7、先按a字段排序，a字段相同按b字段，最后计算排名"></a>7、先按a字段排序，a字段相同按b字段，最后计算排名</h1><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="variable">@cur1</span> :<span class="operator">=</span> <span class="variable">@cur1</span> <span class="operator">+</span> <span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">AS</span> rank,</span><br><span class="line">	p.<span class="operator">*</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span></span><br><span class="line">	(</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">		tts.<span class="operator">*</span>,</span><br><span class="line">		su.nick_name <span class="keyword">AS</span> nick_name </span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">FROM</span></span><br><span class="line">		t_train_score <span class="keyword">AS</span> tts,</span><br><span class="line">		sys_user <span class="keyword">AS</span> su </span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">WHERE</span></span><br><span class="line">		tts.user_no <span class="operator">=</span> su.user_name </span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">AND</span> tts.class_code <span class="operator">=</span> &quot;20220420114&quot; </span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">AND</span> tts.project_code <span class="operator">=</span> &quot;b15f9bd99857461aa256aca27ea60cc4&quot; </span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">AND</span> tts.check_code <span class="operator">=</span> &quot;20220428001&quot; </span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">AND</span> tts.  <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span> </span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">ORDER</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span></span><br><span class="line">		score <span class="keyword">DESC</span>,</span><br><span class="line">		total_time <span class="keyword">ASC</span> </span><br><span class="line">		LIMIT <span class="number">0</span>,</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">		) p,(</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="variable">@cur1</span> :<span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span> #&#123;如果分页的话直接在这去  拿 pageNum<span class="number">-1</span> <span class="operator">*</span> pageSize即可&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	) q</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="8、查询去年1月到12月"><a href="#8、查询去年1月到12月" class="headerlink" title="8、查询去年1月到12月"></a>8、查询去年1月到12月</h1><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">CASE</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">WHEN</span></span><br><span class="line">length( mon ) <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">THEN</span></span><br><span class="line">concat( <span class="keyword">LEFT</span> ( <span class="built_in">CURRENT_DATE</span>, <span class="number">5</span>)<span class="number">-1</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;-0&#x27;</span>, mon ) <span class="keyword">ELSE</span> concat( <span class="keyword">LEFT</span> ( <span class="built_in">CURRENT_DATE</span>, <span class="number">5</span> )<span class="number">-1</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;-&#x27;</span>, mon )</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">END</span> months</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span></span><br><span class="line">( <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="variable">@m</span> :<span class="operator">=</span> <span class="variable">@m</span> <span class="operator">+</span> <span class="number">1</span> mon <span class="keyword">FROM</span> t_mscm_sales, ( <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="variable">@m</span> :<span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span> ) a ) aa</span><br><span class="line">LIMIT <span class="number">12</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="9、查询今年1月到当前月的所有月份"><a href="#9、查询今年1月到当前月的所有月份" class="headerlink" title="9、查询今年1月到当前月的所有月份"></a>9、查询今年1月到当前月的所有月份</h1><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">CASE</span></span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">WHEN</span></span><br><span class="line">		length( mon )<span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">THEN</span></span><br><span class="line">			concat( <span class="keyword">LEFT</span> ( <span class="built_in">CURRENT_DATE</span>, <span class="number">5</span> ), <span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>, mon ) <span class="keyword">ELSE</span> concat( <span class="keyword">LEFT</span> ( <span class="built_in">CURRENT_DATE</span>, <span class="number">5</span> ), mon ) </span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">END</span> months </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span></span><br><span class="line">	( <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="variable">@m</span> :<span class="operator">=</span> <span class="variable">@m</span> <span class="operator">+</span> <span class="number">1</span> mon <span class="keyword">FROM</span> t_mission,( <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="variable">@m</span> :<span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span> ) a ) aa </span><br><span class="line">	LIMIT <span class="number">9</span>; <span class="operator">/</span><span class="operator">/</span><span class="number">9</span>可以随便传</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="10、指定月份生成30天"><a href="#10、指定月份生成30天" class="headerlink" title="10、指定月份生成30天"></a>10、指定月份生成30天</h1><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> date_format(date_add(<span class="string">&#x27;2022-02-01&#x27;</span>, <span class="type">interval</span>(<span class="built_in">cast</span>(help_topic_id <span class="keyword">as</span> signed <span class="type">integer</span>)<span class="operator">+</span> <span class="number">0</span>) <span class="keyword">day</span>),<span class="string">&#x27;%Y-%m-%d&#x27;</span>) 日期</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> mysql.help_topic</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> help_topic_id  <span class="operator">&lt;</span> <span class="keyword">day</span>(last_day(<span class="string">&#x27;2022-02-01&#x27;</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">order</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> help_topic_id;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
